│ distinguishing between vector-only and universal skips, we allow              │
│ planContainsAdditionalSimplifications to recognize legitimate VPlan           │
│ simplifications for this reproducer, preventing the assertion from firing.    │
│ The functional behavior of cost modeling remains unchanged; only the          │
│ diagnostic/assertion guard is corrected to reflect actual simplifications.    │
│ This resolves the crash without weakening the assertion's correctness.\n"     │
│ }                                                                             │
